phrases: We will spend every day at Maid Latte.
We will go to Maid Latte as long as our money lasts.
Our burning soul, hotter than the summer itself, will make this season an unforgettable one!
We are almost there, so chin up, Honoka-chan.
I should not have taken part in the staff trip.
It is the chief's sister's invitation.
Look how big I cut this.
Sis is at the beach, is not she?
I never thought I would win so many.
I cannot finish all of these.
I will call my friends over from the mail in prize club.
But first, let us finish this...
It is been a while, Sis!
You are the manager of a beach house!
She is a tanned version of the Chief.
Relax a bit before you go out on the beach.
I will take care of your belongings, too.
Apparently she opened this place this year.
There is a chair out on the patio.
Girls working at a maid cafe going to a place with blazing UV rays?
You do not care if your skin gets ruined?
Chief's niece, and the popular web idol Aoi.
Are you here to hook up with some men at the beach this time?
What are you thinking, dressing up like that again?
Do not dress in things that make everyone else feel like they are burning up just from looking at you!
Our brother sent him here to become manlier.
I do not like the heat, so I got here early in the morning.
Are you sure you are prepared for the job?
I will be ready for it, since it is for you.
Remember, if you drown, I would not want to let anyone else perform CPR on you.
We will get changed now, Usui-kun.
Well, actually my mother yelled at me to go have fun like other high schoolers do,
so I plan to have all the fun I can.
You really go all out with everything, do not you, Misa-chan?
But... why a swim cap, too?
I guess she is pretty happy to be swimming.
That is definitely the Misa-chan we know.
She is enjoying the ocean to the fullest.
Maybe he was hoping for something?
Well, it is the ocean, so...
Do you want to hang out with us?
We are short on people to play beach volleyball.
He is really not interested in anyone other than Misa-chan.
How many years has it been since I last came to the beach?
When I was in elementary school?
No, probably during the shellfish gathering I did when I was even younger than that.
All right, I am going to have so much fun!
This place actually is not profitable at all.
It is at the end of the beach.
And it is out of the way from everything.
New shop owners do not get a good location that easily.
What a shame, since the shop is new and clean.
How do you expect a downer of a shop like this to become popular?
I hope it goes out of business soon.
He actually looks like a boy.
You have got some nerve to say that.
You do not care what I do to this?
I told you I will once work is over.
Are not you in a pretty bad situation if you do not think of something?
I need something that makes up for the horrible location.
So, something that draws people's eyes.
An attraction that other places do not have.
It is the most powerful weapon in our arsenal, is not it?
You could not possibly be thinking of...
Let us go walk on the beach to advertise.
Yeah, since there are not many people here.
Be careful not to get picked up by dangerous people.
We will just ignore anyone who tries to do that.
Looks like it is time for Aoi-sama to show up.
You go clean up the showers!
Is it all right to let this happen all of a sudden?
We will say it is a today-only event.
Today will be a special day, and tomorrow will be back to normal.
If I get a good turnout, I will remember this as a tactic I can use.
It looks like they are volunteering to do this, so do as you like.
Let me know if you need anything.
A maid cafe has opened by the beach as a limited time event.
Please stop by, Master and Milady.
I will be waiting for you at the Beach House.
Would you like me to take a photo of Master and Milady together?
We have a special limited time menu, too.
Is this really going to be alright?
It is not even used that often!
Why do I have to brush this place when the UV rays are the strongest.
Can I take over the work here?
I thought I would help out as a back stage actor today...
Looks like you are self-conscious about your lack of charm.
Seeing you as a swimsuit maid is boring.
So, can I take over here?
You have cleaning to do inside, right?
Wow, he really hates me, does not he?
The place they were advertising for earlier...
What should I bring for you?
I will have an ice tea.
So this is what a maid cafe is like?
I always wanted to go to one, but I never thought I would find it at a beach.
Good thing we came to the beach today.
I like how earnestly they attend to us.
This is today's limited time menu item, the ocean petit cake set.
Miladies, would you be interested in taking a warm shower?
I have brought you some cold drinks.
If you are ready to order, please let me know.
Over to this seat please, Master.
How about a half-size set for the Young Master?
I got it from the Chief.
Is there an apron I can wear?
I am sorry to do this when this was supposed to be a vacation.
After all, I am always in your debt.
That school swimsuit bothers me in more than one way.
I will let you wear these, so get changed.
I could not really say no.
There are a lot of customers out there, so I had to take it.
Misa-chan, you are going out like that?
Why do not you quit lying around and help out a little?
The tables are packed, and people are waiting to have their order taken.
What do you think you are doing?
Are you sure about this, Misa-chan?
Everyone will see the kiss mark on your back.
Thanks for the hard work, everyone!
I am the one that should be thanking you.
It was the busiest day since I opened this place.
I bet the shop Sis manages is popular, too.
There is free tickets to the onsen.
Let us all go there once we finish eating.
I can even take a dip in an onsen?
What a fabulous summer this is.
This beach is famous for its onsen, too.
This beach is also famous for being haunted.
A couple who decided to commit suicide together were going to jump off a cliff.
But the man actually had another girl on the side, so when they were about to jump,
the guy let the girl jump by herself, and she went to the bottom of the ocean alone.
Several months passed without her body being found.
Then one night, when a couple came here,
A woman covered in blood, crawling up the cliff at an unbelievable speed.
Ever since then, there have been poltergeist sightings around that bush.
I want to see one, too.
That is just rumors getting exaggerated.
So why do you think it is so famous?
Then let us go to the onsen!
It is nice how it is within walking distance.
We will have fun with our girl time.
It is... kind of a bad time for me.
Well, we will not force you, I guess.
It is all your fault, stupid Usui.
If it was not for my back, I would have gone with them.
That is why I stayed behind, too.
Do not think I will forgive you for this crime!
Did you want to go that badly?
I have not gone on a trip in many years.
So I wanted to enjoy it.
I rarely get to go to an onsen.
Besides, it would have distracted me more if I would been with everyone.
Are you scared of the ghost?
I do not want to waste the free onsen ticket the Chief gave us!
Everyone is free ticket got wasted.
I will catch up if I run.
Usui, you better mend the place!
You are going to take it to them?
I do not think you need to do that much.
These let us into an onsen for free when you normally have to pay!
But you might run into a ghost.
I do not believe in such an unrealistic entity.
That is right, they do not exist.
I cannot let them pay money for something unnecessarily because I am scared of such a ridiculous thing.
This beach is also famous for being haunted.
Besides, I have never seen a ghost before in my life.
Why would I believe in them?
I locked up the place, so let us go together.
Where did your strength go, Ayuzawa?
You are making fun of me, are not you?
You plan on teasing me for having another weakness, do not you?
Damn it, let go of me already.
I will be here until you calm down.
What is that supposed to mean?
Could you not flirt in the middle of the street?
So you are playing dumb with me.
Then why were you two hugging in the dark?
You like him, do not you?
I told you that I do not!
Like that, the first day of Maid Latte at the Beach House ended after a hot night.
A bath is a good thing.
Since we came all this way, let us take a dip.
I do not want to go in the men's bath!
So did you take a dip with Aoi-chan, Usui?
I had him in a good lock, but he tricked me.
I had to sneak in because of you.
Enjoy another day at the beach.
And, you will not go to bed yet, right?
I will be telling the scary stories.
